&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant General Surgeons &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;18 Week Support are currently seeking Consultant General Surgeons to support in our growing General Surgery service across the East and South East England regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;18 Week Support are excited to announce that we are supporting the NHS tackle their increasing backlogs in General Surgery by implementing our Insourcing Service over weekends in several NHS Trusts across East and South East England.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consultant General Surgeons&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekend insourced services – Saturdays and Sundays full days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Case mix – Laparoscopic Cholecystectomies and Hernias&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;East and South East England&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekend sessions (full days)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with an excellent Surgical support team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent day rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outside of IR35 (Limited Company pay)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing weekends available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to 18 Week Support Surgical Leadership Team and Head of Nursing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please apply to this post and a member of the 18 Week Support recruitment team specialising in Surgery will be in touch.&lt;/p&gt;
